WEBVTT

00:00:01.459 --> 00:00:03.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRL] Oh, dear, what a waste.</b></Default>

00:00:03.080 --> 00:00:04.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After everything I did</b></Default>

00:00:04.419 --> 00:00:06.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to make her able
to read the room, too.</b></Default>

00:00:06.629 --> 00:00:07.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:00:09.039 --> 00:00:09.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles softly]</b></Default>

00:00:10.460 --> 00:00:12.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How surprising!</b></Default>

00:00:12.169 --> 00:00:14.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you can actually see me.</b></Default>

00:00:14.289 --> 00:00:16.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Guess I gotta hand it
to you, Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:00:18.289 --> 00:00:20.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And who are you, exactly?</b></Default>

00:00:20.079 --> 00:00:22.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, come on</b></Default>

00:00:22.960 --> 00:00:24.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

00:00:24.670 --> 00:00:26.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>'Cause my name</b></Default>

00:00:26.170 --> 00:00:28.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:00:29.960 --> 00:00:32.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what, do you just go
around town in that Santa outfit</b></Default>

00:00:32.829 --> 00:00:35.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>handing out puberty syndrome
to everyone as presents?</b></Default>

00:00:35.539 --> 00:00:36.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, yeah.</b></Default>

00:00:36.579 --> 00:00:39.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Santa Claus's job is to visit
all the nice boys and girls</b></Default>

00:00:39.539 --> 00:00:41.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and pass out presents
to them, you know?</b></Default>

00:00:41.210 --> 00:00:44.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, really? So that means
you showed up in front of me</b></Default>

00:00:44.210 --> 00:00:45.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because I was being nice.</b></Default>

00:00:45.710 --> 00:00:48.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Actually, you were trying
to reveal Santa's true identity.</b></Default>

00:00:49.380 --> 00:00:51.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That puts you
on the naughty list.</b></Default>

00:00:51.960 --> 00:00:54.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think you could
do me a little favor?</b></Default>

00:00:54.289 --> 00:00:55.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is it?</b></Default>

00:00:55.289 --> 00:00:58.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you maybe not pass
those presents out anymore?</b></Default>

00:00:58.579 --> 00:01:00.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Okay.
-Huh?</b></Default>

00:01:00.210 --> 00:01:01.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay?</b></Default>

00:01:01.210 --> 00:01:04.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After all, I'm all out
of presents in my bag of gifts.</b></Default>

00:01:05.209 --> 00:01:07.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on. How many did you have
in there before?</b></Default>

00:01:08.040 --> 00:01:09.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>About this many.</b></Default>

00:01:09.500 --> 00:01:10.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A hundred?</b></Default>

00:01:10.540 --> 00:01:11.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh-uh!</b></Default>

00:01:11.709 --> 00:01:13.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that guess was way off.</b></Default>

00:01:13.290 --> 00:01:15.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You shouldn't
underestimate Santa Claus.</b></Default>

00:01:15.540 --> 00:01:16.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A thousand, then?</b></Default>

00:01:16.829 --> 00:01:18.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Close! About ten million.</b></Default>

00:01:19.500 --> 00:01:20.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:22.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You see, it's that person</b></Default>

00:01:22.879 --> 00:01:24.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that person</b></Default>

00:01:25.040 --> 00:01:26.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and even them.</b></Default>

00:01:26.129 --> 00:01:28.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I gifted presents to everyone.</b></Default>

00:01:28.379 --> 00:01:29.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Santa shouldn't be working</b></Default>

00:01:29.790 --> 00:01:31.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on any days
aside from Christmas.</b></Default>

00:01:31.670 --> 00:01:33.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're the ones
who wanted the presents</b></Default>

00:01:33.750 --> 00:01:35.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so you can't blame me.</b></Default>

00:01:35.040 --> 00:01:37.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles] That girl
was one of them.</b></Default>

00:01:37.420 --> 00:01:38.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:01:43.670 --> 00:01:45.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ opening theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:02:51.500 --> 00:02:57.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:03:13.000 --> 00:03:15.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>OCTOBER 30TH</b></Default>

00:03:16.539 --> 00:03:18.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Question for you, Kunimi.</b></Default>

00:03:18.539 --> 00:03:19.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's up?</b></Default>

00:03:19.629 --> 00:03:21.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}Do you like Miniskirt Santas?</b></Default>

00:03:21.169 --> 00:03:22.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}HEROISM</b></Default>

00:03:22.169 --> 00:03:23.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}No. Not exactly.</b></Default>

00:03:24.039 --> 00:03:25.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. Then do you love them?</b></Default>

00:03:25.750 --> 00:03:27.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Most definitely.</b></Default>

00:03:27.580 --> 00:03:28.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, for instance</b></Default>

00:03:28.750 --> 00:03:31.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you noticed an alluring Santa
in a miniskirt passing by</b></Default>

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:33.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what would you do next?</b></Default>

00:03:33.460 --> 00:03:34.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm. A double take?</b></Default>

00:03:34.919 --> 00:03:35.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, right.</b></Default>

00:03:35.879 --> 00:03:37.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I'd probably gawk at her.</b></Default>

00:03:37.669 --> 00:03:38.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, right.</b></Default>

00:03:38.919 --> 00:03:41.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you boys are done with
your stupid locker room talk</b></Default>

00:03:41.669 --> 00:03:43.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>can we get going now?</b></Default>

00:03:44.210 --> 00:03:45.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know, Sakuta and Futaba</b></Default>

00:03:45.960 --> 00:03:48.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you've both changed
since I last saw you.</b></Default>

00:03:48.289 --> 00:03:50.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've changed
more than we have, Kunimi.</b></Default>

00:03:51.289 --> 00:03:54.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what is it like living as
a heroic firefighter every day?</b></Default>

00:03:54.750 --> 00:03:56.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I go back and forth
from being on duty</b></Default>

00:03:56.830 --> 00:03:58.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for 24 hours straight</b></Default>

00:03:58.750 --> 00:04:01.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I report for duty in the morning
and work till the next morning.</b></Default>

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:04.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I get to be off the clock
an entire day.</b></Default>

00:04:04.419 --> 00:04:05.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on a second.</b></Default>

00:04:05.789 --> 00:04:08.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does that mean you're here
right after a graveyard shift?</b></Default>

00:04:09.039 --> 00:04:10.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you okay physically?</b></Default>

00:04:10.710 --> 00:04:13.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yeah. We take naps
in shifts, so don't worry.</b></Default>

00:04:13.879 --> 00:04:15.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Although we do keep
our uniforms on</b></Default>

00:04:15.750 --> 00:04:17.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so we're able to deploy
at any time.</b></Default>

00:04:17.829 --> 00:04:18.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look at Kunimi.</b></Default>

00:04:18.829 --> 00:04:20.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Already a proper member
of the working force.</b></Default>

00:04:20.879 --> 00:04:22.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, of course I am.</b></Default>

00:04:22.290 --> 00:04:25.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At least enough so I can order
a cauldron sardine bowl</b></Default>

00:04:25.170 --> 00:04:26.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and fried chicken together.</b></Default>

00:04:26.629 --> 00:04:27.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Damn bourgeoisies.</b></Default>

00:04:27.709 --> 00:04:30.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're free
to have some too, Futaba.</b></Default>

00:04:30.459 --> 00:04:32.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIO] Then I'll just take one.</b></Default>

00:04:32.959 --> 00:04:35.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, how's college life
been treating you?</b></Default>

00:04:35.420 --> 00:04:36.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Been having any fun?</b></Default>

00:04:36.920 --> 00:04:38.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From what I've been hearing</b></Default>

00:04:38.420 --> 00:04:41.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>college kids hang out at
hobby clubs and mixers, right?</b></Default>

00:04:41.329 --> 00:04:44.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps that's true for all
other college students but me.</b></Default>

00:04:44.420 --> 00:04:47.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No one has ever even invited me
to a matchmaking party.</b></Default>

00:04:47.329 --> 00:04:50.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa was impossible
to invite 'cause he already has</b></Default>

00:04:50.170 --> 00:04:52.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the prettiest girlfriend
in the world.</b></Default>

00:04:52.170 --> 00:04:54.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, well</b></Default>

00:04:54.129 --> 00:04:55.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you ever been to one?</b></Default>

00:04:55.790 --> 00:04:57.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Absolutely not.</b></Default>

00:04:57.290 --> 00:04:59.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Absolutely? Why not?</b></Default>

00:04:59.170 --> 00:05:01.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But surely you've been invited
to one, right?</b></Default>

00:05:01.829 --> 00:05:03.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course I've been invited.</b></Default>

00:05:03.629 --> 00:05:06.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I had a shift
for my tutoring job on that day.</b></Default>

00:05:06.540 --> 00:05:09.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, so you had a convenient
excuse to decline the offer.</b></Default>

00:05:09.420 --> 00:05:10.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

00:05:10.750 --> 00:05:12.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[phone vibrates]
-Huh?</b></Default>

00:05:12.379 --> 00:05:14.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, it's my classmate.</b></Default>

00:05:14.079 --> 00:05:16.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't worry about us.
Go answer it.</b></Default>

00:05:16.329 --> 00:05:17.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry.</b></Default>

00:05:17.379 --> 00:05:18.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey. What's up?</b></Default>

00:05:19.209 --> 00:05:21.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[YUUMA] Futaba's fully embracing
college life, huh?</b></Default>

00:05:21.790 --> 00:05:24.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] She is
a college student, after all.</b></Default>

00:05:24.079 --> 00:05:25.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[YUUMA] Yeah, that's true.</b></Default>

00:05:25.379 --> 00:05:26.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her pupils at the cram school</b></Default>

00:05:26.959 --> 00:05:29.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>have a lot of respect
for her, too. More than me.</b></Default>

00:05:29.629 --> 00:05:31.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I heard about that.</b></Default>

00:05:31.170 --> 00:05:32.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, from Futaba?</b></Default>

00:05:32.540 --> 00:05:34.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From one
of my basketball juniors.</b></Default>

00:05:34.540 --> 00:05:36.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's actually
one of her students.</b></Default>

00:05:36.459 --> 00:05:38.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'd recognize him
in an instant</b></Default>

00:05:38.170 --> 00:05:39.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because he's taller than me.</b></Default>

00:05:39.750 --> 00:05:43.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, there is one really big
student at the cram school.</b></Default>

00:05:43.209 --> 00:05:44.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, anyway</b></Default>

00:05:44.709 --> 00:05:46.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm glad that both of you
are doing all right</b></Default>

00:05:47.500 --> 00:05:49.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and seem to be having
some fun, too.</b></Default>

00:05:51.750 --> 00:05:54.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Was that a friend on the phone?
-[RIO] Yeah.</b></Default>

00:05:54.290 --> 00:05:57.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've been trying to convince her
to introduce me to them</b></Default>

00:05:57.290 --> 00:05:59.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but she's not
letting me meet them.</b></Default>

00:05:59.129 --> 00:06:00.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How many times do I have to say</b></Default>

00:06:00.790 --> 00:06:03.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I have no reason
to introduce them to you?</b></Default>

00:06:03.170 --> 00:06:06.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have to vet them to make sure
they're taking good care of you.</b></Default>

00:06:06.170 --> 00:06:08.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-That's right.
-[sighs]</b></Default>

00:06:09.420 --> 00:06:10.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll ask next time.</b></Default>

00:06:10.959 --> 00:06:12.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. For real?</b></Default>

00:06:12.709 --> 00:06:14.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIO] Yeah. I'll just ask</b></Default>

00:06:14.170 --> 00:06:16.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if they'd like to meet two guys
who have girlfriends.</b></Default>

00:06:16.920 --> 00:06:19.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] You're never gonna
let us meet them, are you?</b></Default>

00:06:19.670 --> 00:06:21.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Kunimi laughs]</b></Default>

00:06:21.629 --> 00:06:24.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Enoshima's still on land.
So wicked.</b></Default>

00:06:24.250 --> 00:06:25.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The photo's good, too.</b></Default>

00:06:25.629 --> 00:06:27.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KUNIMI] We should
take a picture, too.</b></Default>

00:06:30.709 --> 00:06:33.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shall title this piece
"Arrival at Enoshima."</b></Default>

00:06:33.920 --> 00:06:35.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should get back
on the mainland.</b></Default>

00:06:35.879 --> 00:06:38.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Any longer, and this area
will be underwater.</b></Default>

00:06:38.420 --> 00:06:40.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. We'd better
head back soon.</b></Default>

00:06:40.500 --> 00:06:42.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I gotta get to work after this.</b></Default>

00:06:42.629 --> 00:06:43.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIO] And Kunimi</b></Default>

00:06:43.709 --> 00:06:46.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you're off duty</b></Default>

00:06:48.040 --> 00:06:50.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[KUNIMI] By the way, Sakuta...
-Hm?</b></Default>

00:06:50.959 --> 00:06:52.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You got something to tell me?</b></Default>

00:06:53.209 --> 00:06:55.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good job working hard
in your six-month training.</b></Default>

00:06:55.750 --> 00:06:58.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And congrats on earning a spot
in a brigade.</b></Default>

00:06:58.750 --> 00:07:00.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that enough?</b></Default>

00:07:00.129 --> 00:07:02.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yep, like I thought</b></Default>

00:07:02.709 --> 00:07:03.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Noticed what?</b></Default>

00:07:03.709 --> 00:07:05.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll stay quiet for now.</b></Default>

00:07:05.750 --> 00:07:07.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think it'll be
more interesting that way.</b></Default>

00:07:09.379 --> 00:07:11.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIO] {\i1}Being a firefighter{\i0}
{\i1}seems like hard work.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:07:12.329 --> 00:07:14.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] {\i1}It suits Kunimi</b></Default>

00:07:14.329 --> 00:07:17.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The same can't be said
for you, Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:07:17.209 --> 00:07:19.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, well, my dream
is to become Santa Claus</b></Default>

00:07:19.629 --> 00:07:20.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'm okay with that.</b></Default>

00:07:20.879 --> 00:07:23.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe saying stuff like that
is what caused you</b></Default>

00:07:23.329 --> 00:07:25.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to see an illusion
of a Miniskirt Santa.</b></Default>

00:07:25.790 --> 00:07:28.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So? What do you think
that was all about?</b></Default>

00:07:28.379 --> 00:07:31.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Considering you are the only
person who was able to see her</b></Default>

00:07:31.420 --> 00:07:34.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this case sounds rather similar
to that of Sakurajima's.</b></Default>

00:07:34.920 --> 00:07:35.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

00:07:36.329 --> 00:07:38.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did a fair amount
of online research</b></Default>

00:07:38.290 --> 00:07:40.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into Touko Kirishima as well</b></Default>

00:07:40.329 --> 00:07:42.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but all the results
that came up in the search</b></Default>

00:07:42.709 --> 00:07:45.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>only gave me rumors
with no reliable credibility.</b></Default>

00:07:45.329 --> 00:07:46.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I heard there's one</b></Default>

00:07:46.879 --> 00:07:48.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that said her true identity
was Mai.</b></Default>

00:07:48.879 --> 00:07:51.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIO] When you look
from another perspective</b></Default>

00:07:51.209 --> 00:07:52.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>no information
coming out these days</b></Default>

00:07:53.040 --> 00:07:54.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>might be even more unnatural.</b></Default>

00:07:55.170 --> 00:07:56.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because the names
of perpetrators</b></Default>

00:07:56.879 --> 00:07:59.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that news outlets and newspapers
don't disclose</b></Default>

00:07:59.290 --> 00:08:01.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are plastered
all over the internet.</b></Default>

