00:13:47.129 --> 00:13:48.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIORI] I see.</b></Default>

00:13:48.379 --> 00:13:49.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, then.</b></Default>

00:13:50.210 --> 00:13:51.129 line:90% align:center
