<Default><b>from constantly arguing
with somebody else.</b></Default>

00:14:16.169 --> 00:14:18.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I got invited
to another mixer today, too.</b></Default>

00:14:18.539 --> 00:14:21.289 line:90% align:center
