handsome med school students.</b></Default>

00:14:21.379 --> 00:14:23.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come to think of it</b></Default>

00:14:23.830 --> 00:14:26.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how your so-called friends
