00:14:26.539 --> 00:14:28.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-for your boyfriend-less self.
-Yeah.</b></Default>

00:14:28.460 --> 00:14:30.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hard to say no because
they're doing it for me.</b></Default>

00:14:30.789 --> 00:14:32.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are in college now</b></Default>

00:14:32.330 --> 00:14:34.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so you got to navigate
relations well, don't you?</b></Default>

00:14:34.879 --> 00:14:37.629 line:90% align:center
