00:14:46.379 --> 00:14:47.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so take your time.</b></Default>

00:14:48.169 --> 00:14:49.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Too bad for you, Fukuyama.</b></Default>

00:14:50.330 --> 00:14:51.289 line:90% align:center
