00:15:00.879 --> 00:15:03.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I had that confidence</b></Default>

00:15:03.960 --> 00:15:05.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But anyway, are you free today?</b></Default>

00:15:05.919 --> 00:15:07.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going to a mixer</b></Default>

00:15:07.379 --> 00:15:09.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but someone got a cold</b></Default>

00:15:09.830 --> 00:15:12.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't know.
Aren't guys who have girlfriends</b></Default>

00:15:12.419 --> 00:15:14.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>like a wet blanket
at those kinds of places?</b></Default>

00:15:14.710 --> 00:15:17.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd really appreciate it</b></Default>

00:15:17.669 --> 00:15:19.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on, Azusagawa, please?</b></Default>

00:15:19.289 --> 00:15:21.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, all the girls
are in nursing, man!</b></Default>

00:15:21.460 --> 00:15:22.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're nursing?</b></Default>

00:15:22.460 --> 00:15:24.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not like that. They're nurses.</b></Default>

00:15:24.330 --> 00:15:26.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Give me a little more
hype, please.</b></Default>

00:15:26.169 --> 00:15:27.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Future ones, right?</b></Default>

00:15:27.789 --> 00:15:30.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No way. You mean
you aren't into nurses?</b></Default>

00:15:30.330 --> 00:15:33.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd join without hesitation
if it was a Miniskirt Santa.</b></Default>

00:15:33.539 --> 00:15:34.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's also nice.</b></Default>

00:15:34.710 --> 00:15:36.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But seriously</b></Default>

00:15:36.960 --> 00:15:39.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you okay with me not finding
a cute girlfriend who's a nurse?</b></Default>

00:15:39.379 --> 00:15:40.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I couldn't care less.</b></Default>

00:15:40.580 --> 00:15:41.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't be like that!</b></Default>

00:15:42.039 --> 00:15:44.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Regardless, Mai would
never authorize it</b></Default>

00:15:44.289 --> 00:15:45.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the first place.</b></Default>

00:15:45.460 --> 00:15:46.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right, then.</b></Default>

00:15:46.460 --> 00:15:48.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would it be okay
if you got her permission?</b></Default>

00:15:49.419 --> 00:15:50.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] {\i1}Why don't you go?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:15:50.710 --> 00:15:52.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] No. Shouldn't I not?</b></Default>

00:15:52.169 --> 00:15:55.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Think about it, Sakuta.
If you miss this opportunity</b></Default>

00:15:55.080 --> 00:15:56.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you might never get
a chance again.</b></Default>

00:15:56.960 --> 00:15:59.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if that's true</b></Default>

00:15:59.539 --> 00:16:01.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're my girlfriend after all.</b></Default>

00:16:01.330 --> 00:16:04.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}And as your girlfriend</b></Default>

00:16:04.500 --> 00:16:07.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You did say the girls
are in nursing, didn't you?</b></Default>

00:16:07.330 --> 00:16:09.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Isn't Akagi studying
to be a nurse as well?</b></Default>

00:16:10.129 --> 00:16:11.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, she is, but...</b></Default>

00:16:11.919 --> 00:16:13.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}It's a good chance{\i0}
{\i1}to learn something.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:16:13.919 --> 00:16:15.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:16:15.330 --> 00:16:17.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[doors beeping]</b></Default>

00:16:17.580 --> 00:16:20.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, man. My nerves
are starting to get to me.</b></Default>

00:16:20.330 --> 00:16:22.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's a good way
to relieve your anxiety.</b></Default>

00:16:22.919 --> 00:16:23.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh? Like what?</b></Default>

00:16:24.039 --> 00:16:26.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>First you start by putting
both of your index fingers</b></Default>

00:16:26.919 --> 00:16:29.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-at the edge of your mouth.
-Like this?</b></Default>

00:16:29.250 --> 00:16:32.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And then stretch out your mouth
by pulling them outwards.</b></Default>

00:16:32.210 --> 00:16:33.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like this?</b></Default>

00:16:33.169 --> 00:16:35.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Keep your fingers there
and say, "Kanazawa-bunko."</b></Default>

00:16:36.169 --> 00:16:37.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kanazawa-unko.</b></Default>

00:16:44.669 --> 00:16:45.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] You can use
that unko joke</b></Default>

00:16:46.039 --> 00:16:48.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you run out of things
to talk about at the mixer.</b></Default>

00:16:48.960 --> 00:16:49.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] Thanks</b></Default>

00:16:49.960 --> 00:16:51.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I'll do my best
and not resort to your poo joke.</b></Default>

00:16:52.419 --> 00:16:53.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Quite a few people out here.</b></Default>

00:16:53.919 --> 00:16:55.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is Halloween after all.</b></Default>

00:16:55.500 --> 00:16:57.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa</b></Default>

00:16:57.629 --> 00:16:59.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I stray, I'll just go home.</b></Default>

00:16:59.710 --> 00:17:01.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why I'm telling you.</b></Default>

00:17:01.129 --> 00:17:02.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Then what?
Want to hold hands?</b></Default>

00:17:02.960 --> 00:17:04.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] What? No way!</b></Default>

00:17:05.329 --> 00:17:07.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey there. I'm Ryohei Kodani.</b></Default>

00:17:07.250 --> 00:17:09.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm a sophomore
in international commerce.</b></Default>

00:17:09.750 --> 00:17:12.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Hello.
I'm Sakuta Azusagawa</b></Default>

00:17:12.630 --> 00:17:14.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a freshman majoring
in statistical science.</b></Default>

00:17:14.880 --> 00:17:16.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Two girls coming tonight
let me know</b></Default>

00:17:16.789 --> 00:17:18.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they just arrived
at the station.</b></Default>

00:17:18.670 --> 00:17:20.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The other's gonna be late</b></Default>

00:17:20.130 --> 00:17:21.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so we'll get started
once those two get here.</b></Default>

00:17:22.000 --> 00:17:25.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I gotta admit</b></Default>

00:17:25.329 --> 00:17:27.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've been wanting to talk to you
on a personal level.</b></Default>

00:17:28.039 --> 00:17:29.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not being targeted, am I?</b></Default>

00:17:29.789 --> 00:17:32.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No way. Why would you be?
[laughs]</b></Default>

00:17:32.130 --> 00:17:34.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Good evening.
-Good evening, boys.</b></Default>

00:17:34.420 --> 00:17:37.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RYOHEI] Oh, we've been waiting.
Please, please, sit down.</b></Default>

00:17:37.329 --> 00:17:40.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Okay. Excuse me.
-Pardon me.</b></Default>

00:17:41.130 --> 00:17:43.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[laughter]
-[RYOHEI] Yeah, for real.</b></Default>

00:17:43.289 --> 00:17:45.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And the karaoke party
was a big hit with everyone.</b></Default>

00:17:46.039 --> 00:17:48.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRL 1] What kind of songs
do you sing, Kodani?</b></Default>

00:17:48.750 --> 00:17:51.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Recently, I'd say...
Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:17:51.829 --> 00:17:53.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Seriously?
That's such a surprise!</b></Default>

00:17:53.789 --> 00:17:55.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm totally in love
with this song.</b></Default>

00:17:56.000 --> 00:18:00.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ Touko's song playing]</b></Default>

00:18:00.829 --> 00:18:01.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah, yes.</b></Default>

00:18:02.000 --> 00:18:03.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her transparent voice
is so great.</b></Default>

00:18:04.039 --> 00:18:06.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the way, the other girl
just made it to the station.</b></Default>

00:18:06.880 --> 00:18:09.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, I guess she's about
ten minutes away from here?</b></Default>

00:18:09.460 --> 00:18:10.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, that's right.</b></Default>

00:18:10.880 --> 00:18:13.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Take a look at this.
I wrote this one.</b></Default>

00:18:13.079 --> 00:18:16.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It looks like one of my DREAMING
posts really came true!</b></Default>

00:18:16.079 --> 00:18:18.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRL 1] You go to matchmaking
parties every week.</b></Default>

00:18:18.710 --> 00:18:20.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course it'd come true.</b></Default>

00:18:20.079 --> 00:18:22.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRL 2] But I wrote this
a month ago.</b></Default>

00:18:22.079 --> 00:18:24.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What does that pound sign
DREAMING mean?</b></Default>

00:18:24.920 --> 00:18:27.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not a pound sign.
They're called hashtags.</b></Default>

00:18:27.500 --> 00:18:29.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa isn't keen
on this stuff</b></Default>

00:18:29.460 --> 00:18:31.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because he doesn't
have a smartphone.</b></Default>

00:18:31.380 --> 00:18:32.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-For real?
-Why not?</b></Default>

00:18:33.210 --> 00:18:35.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what is this DREAMING thing?</b></Default>

00:18:35.960 --> 00:18:38.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've heard my cram school
students talking about it too.</b></Default>

00:18:38.789 --> 00:18:41.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Originally, it was a hashtag
that people used</b></Default>

00:18:41.210 --> 00:18:44.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to describe the dreams they had
and talk about them with others.</b></Default>

00:18:44.539 --> 00:18:47.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TAKUMI] Oh, and by the way</b></Default>

00:18:47.380 --> 00:18:49.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to show you're talking
about a particular topic.</b></Default>

00:18:49.829 --> 00:18:51.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRL 1] But recently</b></Default>

00:18:51.880 --> 00:18:54.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that a bunch of people's posts
are becoming prophetic dreams.</b></Default>

00:18:55.039 --> 00:18:56.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RYOHEI] I've done
some research, too.</b></Default>

00:18:56.960 --> 00:18:59.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Scandals involving celebrities
were spot on</b></Default>

00:18:59.420 --> 00:19:01.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and disasters
caused by heavy rain happened.</b></Default>

00:19:01.829 --> 00:19:04.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's like these dreams
really were prophetic.</b></Default>

00:19:04.250 --> 00:19:06.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRL 2] And my dream
of a matchmaking party.</b></Default>

00:19:06.829 --> 00:19:09.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So their dreams that came true
like a prophecy...</b></Default>

00:19:09.630 --> 00:19:11.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think
they believe you, Chiharu.</b></Default>

00:19:11.789 --> 00:19:14.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, then. For instance</b></Default>

00:19:14.420 --> 00:19:17.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about something happening
in this neighborhood today.</b></Default>

00:19:18.039 --> 00:19:19.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-There is one!
-What is it?</b></Default>

00:19:19.880 --> 00:19:21.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"A dream where I dress
as a fallen angel</b></Default>

00:19:21.920 --> 00:19:23.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for the Sakuragicho
Halloween party</b></Default>

00:19:23.789 --> 00:19:26.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and my boyfriend
in a devil costume kisses me."</b></Default>

00:19:26.329 --> 00:19:27.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who even cares?</b></Default>

00:19:27.539 --> 00:19:28.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, here's another one.</b></Default>

00:19:28.920 --> 00:19:31.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"I dreamt that
in the Sakuragicho courtyard</b></Default>

00:19:31.170 --> 00:19:33.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the big Jack-o'-lantern
came falling down.</b></Default>

00:19:33.539 --> 00:19:36.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A girl wearing a Red Riding Hood
costume got injured.</b></Default>

00:19:36.420 --> 00:19:38.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Horrible dream</b></Default>

00:19:38.500 --> 00:19:41.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There were a ton of people
at the train station.</b></Default>

00:19:41.079 --> 00:19:42.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, hey, by the way</b></Default>

00:19:42.329 --> 00:19:44.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa, you're not going
on a Halloween date?</b></Default>

00:19:45.039 --> 00:19:47.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Huh?
-Wait, that's right!</b></Default>

00:19:47.170 --> 00:19:50.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it true that you're going out
with Mai Sakurajima?</b></Default>

00:19:50.130 --> 00:19:51.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, no. I'm not.</b></Default>

00:19:51.539 --> 00:19:54.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I thought you were.
-You are dating her, though!</b></Default>

00:19:54.079 --> 00:19:55.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, so you are, huh?</b></Default>

00:19:55.210 --> 00:19:57.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm jealous that
you're dating someone like her.</b></Default>

00:19:57.630 --> 00:19:58.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After I saw that movie</b></Default>

00:19:58.920 --> 00:20:00.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I registered
to be an organ donor.</b></Default>

00:20:00.710 --> 00:20:02.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That drama series
is one of my favorites.</b></Default>

00:20:02.960 --> 00:20:05.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The one with that unsociable
high school detective</b></Default>

00:20:05.829 --> 00:20:08.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who makes bento boxes
for the perps every episode.</b></Default>

00:20:08.539 --> 00:20:10.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Believe it or not</b></Default>

00:20:10.789 --> 00:20:12.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for Mai Sakurajima's
partner role</b></Default>

00:20:12.420 --> 00:20:13.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>back in middle school.</b></Default>

00:20:13.630 --> 00:20:15.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Seriously?
-But, like</b></Default>

00:20:15.289 --> 00:20:17.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what do you have to do
to date actual celebrities?</b></Default>

00:20:18.039 --> 00:20:20.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In my case, you go
to the same high school.</b></Default>

00:20:20.579 --> 00:20:22.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That alone isn't enough
to get a date, though.</b></Default>

00:20:22.880 --> 00:20:24.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What I mean is</b></Default>

00:20:26.210 --> 00:20:28.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, in the middle of
mid-term exams, I snuck out.</b></Default>

00:20:29.039 --> 00:20:30.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRLS] You snuck out, and?</b></Default>

00:20:30.579 --> 00:20:32.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I went out to the courtyard
while it was empty.</b></Default>

00:20:33.000 --> 00:20:34.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALL] Yeah, and?</b></Default>

00:20:34.750 --> 00:20:37.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To confess my feelings</b></Default>

00:20:37.210 --> 00:20:39.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>loud enough so that
everyone was able to hear me.</b></Default>

00:20:39.539 --> 00:20:41.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you really?</b></Default>

00:20:41.170 --> 00:20:43.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Yep. It's all true.
-[BOTH] Huh?</b></Default>

00:20:43.250 --> 00:20:45.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I saw the whole thing
from my classroom.</b></Default>

00:20:46.000 --> 00:20:47.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry I'm so late.</b></Default>

00:20:47.380 --> 00:20:50.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm a freshman in nursing.
Saki Kamisato.</b></Default>

00:20:50.579 --> 00:20:53.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa over there and I
were classmates in high school.</b></Default>

00:20:53.880 --> 00:20:56.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[CHIHARU] Well, Saki</b></Default>

00:20:56.420 --> 00:20:58.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That means you know
Mai Sakurajima, too?</b></Default>

00:20:59.130 --> 00:21:02.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on. Is this what Kunimi
was alluding to the other day?</b></Default>

00:21:03.960 --> 00:21:06.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, all right. We're heading
to the after party now.</b></Default>

00:21:06.710 --> 00:21:08.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See you later, Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:21:09.170 --> 00:21:10.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

00:21:11.710 --> 00:21:14.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, then.
I'm taking the subway home.</b></Default>

00:21:14.329 --> 00:21:15.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:21:15.960 --> 00:21:18.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Kunimi is getting
an earful about this.</b></Default>

00:21:30.539 --> 00:21:31.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:21:37.039 --> 00:21:38.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both grunt]</b></Default>

00:21:38.130 --> 00:21:39.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:21:41.329 --> 00:21:42.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Akagi?</b></Default>

00:21:46.000 --> 00:21:47.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry. Gotta go.</b></Default>

00:21:59.130 --> 00:22:00.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mommy!</b></Default>

00:22:00.130 --> 00:22:02.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want a picture
with the pumpkin!</b></Default>

00:22:05.420 --> 00:22:06.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, wait! Come back!</b></Default>

00:22:15.460 --> 00:22:17.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hey, are you okay?
-Uh-huh.</b></Default>

00:22:17.920 --> 00:22:19.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mio! Are you hurt anywhere?</b></Default>

00:22:19.880 --> 00:22:20.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I'm fine.</b></Default>

00:22:21.420 --> 00:22:23.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAN] Thank you very much.</b></Default>

00:22:23.079 --> 00:22:24.329 line:90% align:center
